    "body": "Denial of service protection; or you could make the tx pool do excessive work by sending thousands of txs with the gas only going up by a gwei each time; instead there is an escalating cost to it e.g. an example is the txn pool churn that caused Geth's outage on the Goerli testnet on Mar 13th https://twitter.com/vdWijden/status/1635218368155488262 (Nethermind didn't have an outage)\r\n",
